        {
            "title": "曾志偉搵AI代答72歲生日慶祝情形  大讚新科技冇脾氣兼24小時任用  影響將來電影電視發展",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"曾志偉今日（15日）出席香港影視娛樂行業Ai策略合作發布會。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2aabff1b908a915200a79113f85df920/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041515150822759.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">曾志偉今日（15日）出席香港影視娛樂行業Ai策略合作發布會。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>曾志偉今日（15日）出席香港影視娛樂行業Ai策略合作發布會，志偉即場與「AI曾志偉」互動，司儀問志偉昨日如何慶祝生日，AI曾志偉代答表示昨日過得很開心，很多朋友一起慶祝，還有美味食物和搞笑遊戲，朋友更為他獻唱，感到驚喜又感動。AI曾志偉更以日文、韓文及阿拉伯文回答現場嘉賓的提問。\n\n</p><h2>想搵AI為代言餅店做廣告</h2>\n<p>談到AI的幕後製作，志偉表示自己對此感興趣，亦令他想起可以此技術為其代言的餅店做廣告。他說現時政府很多機構也採用AI技術提供資訊，AI回答提問時不會衝動或不耐煩，被鬧仍很溫柔回答，不會發脾氣，24小時任勞任怨。他表示在電視電影方面，AI影響將來的事，又稱今次錄製AI片段只是簡單地穿上西裝，不需要說話，AI已能為他開口以不同言語說話。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"談到AI的幕後製作，志偉表示自己對此感興趣。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ec01c6bffcc9a02927dcbc9ed619e139/2025-04/IMG-20250415-WA0047.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        談到AI的幕後製作，志偉表示自己對此感興趣。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"志偉即場與「AI曾志偉」互動。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9246660a63882f2c268394470b4d7695/2025-04/IMG-20250415-WA0048.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        志偉即場與「AI曾志偉」互動。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"儀問志偉昨日如何慶祝生日，AI曾志偉代答表示昨日過得很開心。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b18e8d81aecd9205852a5fbf29767efc/2025-04/IMG-20250415-WA0049.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        儀問志偉昨日如何慶祝生日，AI曾志偉代答表示昨日過得很開心。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"AI曾志偉更以日文、韓文及阿拉伯文回答現場嘉賓的提問。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/55222db8187a0032715612067e9376bf/2025-04/IMG-20250415-WA0050.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        AI曾志偉更以日文、韓文及阿拉伯文回答現場嘉賓的提問。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曾志偉想起可以此技術為其代言的餅店做廣告。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a6c61e1591982965c3ac59622ceee435/2025-04/IMG-20250415-WA0051.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曾志偉想起可以此技術為其代言的餅店做廣告。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"他說現時政府很多機構也採用AI技術提供資訊。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/79a688eabfb6743185a9a69a1f00c934/2025-04/IMG-20250415-WA0052.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        他說現時政府很多機構也採用AI技術提供資訊。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"他大讚AI回答提問時不會衝動或不耐煩，被鬧仍很溫柔回答，不會發脾氣。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/24f451b91179db391b66453928782e46/2025-04/IMG-20250415-WA0053.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        他大讚AI回答提問時不會衝動或不耐煩，被鬧仍很溫柔回答，不會發脾氣。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"而且24小時任勞任怨。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/345bc5b3258e1712811227ab559a61a1/2025-04/IMG-20250415-WA0054.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        而且24小時任勞任怨。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"他表示在電視電影方面，AI影響將來的事。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f98d2ead00258339c8d068da624e82e0/2025-04/IMG-20250415-WA0055.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        他表示在電視電影方面，AI影響將來的事。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曾志偉又稱今次錄製AI片段只是簡單地穿上西裝，不需要說話。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/df17f7e0019df414de0fa0769dce4132/2025-04/IMG-20250415-WA0056.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曾志偉又稱今次錄製AI片段只是簡單地穿上西裝，不需要說話。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
