        {
            "title": "英超｜般尼茅夫1球小勝富咸 眾將劍指歐戰席位",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"般尼茅夫1:0富咸。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5085dfe198ac33383059e7e4fe38ab4e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041514271654084.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">般尼茅夫1:0富咸。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>般尼茅夫於周一英超靠施曼尤射入全場唯一入球，主場1:0擊敗富咸，終止英超6場不敗劣勢。更重要的是，般尼茅夫賽後追至與富咸同分，並以較佳得失球壓過對方升上第8，眾將即明言全力衝擊來季歐戰席位。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"施曼尤(右)射入全場唯一入球。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/91796f5ca3612d1b65d23cd16d833eb0/2025-04/2025-04-14T190351Z_688216685_UP1EL4E1GYD72_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BOU-FUL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        施曼尤(右)射入全場唯一入球。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"般尼茅夫(紅黑衫)1:0富咸。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/16491cab8bc054230dc566a7cb6bc4f5/2025-04/2025-04-14T191042Z_473401159_UP1EL4E1H9S7E_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BOU-FUL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        般尼茅夫(紅黑衫)1:0富咸。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"般尼茅夫(紅黑衫)1:0富咸。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3b7547ac30dc9dabf158d10f68dc9296/2025-04/2025-04-14T193912Z_1620840747_UP1EL4E1ILA8F_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BOU-FUL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        般尼茅夫(紅黑衫)1:0富咸。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"般尼茅夫(紅黑衫)1:0富咸。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c318b38f33d645ad158a8cc6e22e75bf/2025-04/2025-04-14T200957Z_1955741092_UP1EL4E1K0G92_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BOU-FUL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        般尼茅夫(紅黑衫)1:0富咸。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"般尼茅夫(紅黑衫)1:0富咸。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/88b0452687c0fe8dd96f8945b800d98d/2025-04/2025-04-14T202558Z_1973888199_UP1EL4E1KR99T_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BOU-FUL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        般尼茅夫(紅黑衫)1:0富咸。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"般尼茅夫(紅黑衫)1:0富咸。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0cf034c963c384f81f8e9062efb769a2/2025-04/2025-04-14T205321Z_1216229040_UP1EL4E1M0VAM_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BOU-FUL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        般尼茅夫(紅黑衫)1:0富咸。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"般尼茅夫升上第8位。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e7728bad63bd4d7674fd6c92591615f1/2025-04/2025-04-14T205911Z_175979950_UP1EL4E1MAMAO_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BOU-FUL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        般尼茅夫升上第8位。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"般尼茅夫升上第8位。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d6ba69ebedc0b2da506c7e7f22fe30ac/2025-04/2025-04-14T210006Z_1291834717_UP1EL4E1MC4AR_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-BOU-FUL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        般尼茅夫升上第8位。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>般尼茅夫小勝上第8</h2>\n<p>般尼茅夫開賽不足1分鐘就靠施曼尤士哥開紀錄，之後他們成功頂住富咸的反撲，最終靠此入球主場以1:0小勝，取得自2月中以來首場英超勝仗。般尼茅夫全取3分後，與富咸和白禮頓同得48分，前者靠較佳得失球升上第8，一同落後第7位的阿士東維拉6分。\n\n</p><h2>眾將劍指歐戰席位</h2>\n<p>英超第7將可出戰下季歐協聯，故入球功臣施曼尤矢言：「這是一場重要的勝利，尤其我們過去幾場踢得很掙扎。我們今季令不少前列球隊吃苦頭，所以我認為己隊絕對值得一個歐戰席位。」中堅候臣認同道：「很開心能取得勝利，令我們重返爭歐洲賽資格的行列。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
