a-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4114031/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7861286e92c05d72474a51191ae9b622/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250302_231412595.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4114034/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"不少市民對於新光結業感到不捨，今日專程到場打卡影相留念。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2859663ec53ac367e863fd0b7e3fda5f/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250302_231030665.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        不少市民對於新光結業感到不捨，今日專程到場打卡影相留念。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4114035/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"屹立北角52年的粵劇殿堂新光戲院，將於明日正式熄燈拉閘，曲終人散。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/539ca2b1e07283d0219b84fcc2587bb9/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250302_231004485.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        屹立北角52年的粵劇殿堂新光戲院，將於明日正式熄燈拉閘，曲終人散。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4114036/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"不少市民對於新光結業感到不捨，今日專程到場打卡影相留念。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/da0ee8cbdec88ae1d27be7c44e4276d1/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250302_230957324.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        不少市民對於新光結業感到不捨，今日專程到場打卡影相留念。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4114040/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"粵劇殿堂新光戲院屹立北角52年。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6f0917ccd10ce574da10c3189b51dfdf/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250302_230947438.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        粵劇殿堂新光戲院屹立北角52年。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4114041/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"粵劇殿堂新光戲院屹立北角52年。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4b28287de99fcb20989ddfff1f353191/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250302_230941324.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        粵劇殿堂新光戲院屹立北角52年。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4114108/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"張氏姊妹小時候曾在新光戲院看電影，對戲院結業感可惜。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/df94b7c2d74c208d4f50c528f7c4d622/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-03-00-22-54.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        張氏姊妹小時候曾在新光戲院看電影，對戲院結業感可惜。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4114109/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"何先生對新光戲院的建築特別感興趣，認為是北角標誌性的建築。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/54af8ae2383197c86dd0ec0b2c9961e6/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-03-00-23-11.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        何先生對新光戲院的建築特別感興趣，認為是北角標誌性的建築。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<h2>李居明看好黃埔區風水極佳</h2>\n<p>李居明表示，看好黃埔區人傑地靈，風水極佳，為九運具發展潛力的文化地標，故決定將新光文化精神在此區延續。他指，黃埔天地不僅是黃埔站的購物娛樂熱點，更是本地及環球美食的匯聚地，飲食選擇多元化，交通四通八達，與港鐵黃埔站零距離，加上充裕的泊車位，配套非常完善。\n\n</p>\n<p>日後，「新光黃埔」大堂附設新光紀念博物展示區，公開給入場前參觀。隨著戲院的進駐，可以讓新光精神更適切地融入到生活與社區當中，吸引更多人參與文化的傳承之餘，亦打造了文化娛樂的新地標。\n\n</p>\n<p>李居明表示，隨著「新光黃埔」的開業，第一步計劃已成功落實，將成立電影及粵劇兩大宣傳發展基金，為本土製作的電影及粵劇提供宣傳贊助，推廣及支持觀眾進入黃埔天地新地標，致力打造成九龍一個新的娛樂消費社區，刺激本土文化經濟，一系列活化電影及表演文化的具體新計劃將於開幕時公佈，為香港本土娛樂文化打上一枝強心針。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173634/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃埔是本地及環球美食的匯聚地。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/98da7889abccc44b8046ac36f2a5f171/2025-04/0_sH02EDh6eibBIilq.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃埔是本地及環球美食的匯聚地。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173635/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"新址佔地約5萬方呎，租約期3年。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ba794615546f3bc0b37e680644a80c4a/2025-04/53751536134504S8_WGP.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        新址佔地約5萬方呎，租約期3年。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173636/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃埔天地四通八達，與港鐵黃埔站零距離。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/700ccf6fa911bf768a311ed78cae8643/2025-04/201612191843472869.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃埔天地四通八達，與港鐵黃埔站零距離。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173637/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"4院聯演可提供1,200座位，為九龍區電影龍頭戲院之一。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f77cd7333d500817d85599d8e4b16e46/2025-04/202105141219047807.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        4院聯演可提供1,200座位，為九龍區電影龍頭戲院之一。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173638/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"嘉禾黃埔共有4間極具水平的戲院。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d035a0cbaed71c60368204b415b6817/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_6_12_59_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        嘉禾黃埔共有4間極具水平的戲院。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>現時嘉禾黃埔共有4間極具水平的戲院，各有300個座位，四院聯演可提供1,200個座位，為九龍區電影龍頭戲院之一，待具體計劃落實後將改動成更合適的表演場地。紅磡黃埔無論設施和交通配套都非常完善，老中青三代觀眾均喜到場。李居明亦看好2026年世界及香港電影的復甦，開幕後必有活化戲院的新意象。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
